  "Stays the same": "",
  "Formula — f' = f × (v ± v_o)/(v ∓ v_s), where v is speed of sound, v_o is observer speed, v_s is source speed. For Sound Source approaching : Wavelength compressed → higher frequency (higher pitch). The other options — 'Decreases', 'Stays the same', and 'Becomes inaudible' — are related concepts but do not correctly answer this specific question.": "",
